<h2 id="ogrenciler-icin-meditasyon-ve-rahatlama-teknikleri" class="wp-block-heading">Meditation and Relaxation Techniques for Students</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Meditation and relaxation techniques are important for coping with stress and maintaining mental health. Here are some suggestions:</p>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">1. <strong>Breathing Exercises:</strong> You can calm your mind by breathing in and out deeply. This helps you relax during stressful moments.</p>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">2. <strong>Walking Meditation:</strong> While walking outside, you can clear your mind by noticing the sounds and sights around you.</p>
