<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Most public schools in the majority of the world practice co-education.</li>
<li>However, in some countries, schools offering single-sex education still exist for religious or cultural reasons.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Advantages</h3>
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Promotes equality between genders.</li>
<li>Strengthens social interaction and communication skills.</li>
<li>Helps break down stereotypes.</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Disadvantages</h3>
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>It may face resistance in some cultures.</li>
<li>Gender-based differences in attention and behavior can affect the learning environment.</li>
</ul>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-05-22T07:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-16T19:52:26Z') WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'co-education-models-and-opportunities-in-turkey' );
