y.com/en/statistical-analysis-and-data-processing-methods-in-turkey/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<h2 id="turkiyede-istatistiksel-analiz-egitimi-firsatlar-ve-secenekler" class="wp-block-heading">Statistical Analysis Education in Turkey: Opportunities and Options</h2>
