<p>Since these programs in Turkey accept students through standardized tests like <b>ALES</b> (Academic Personnel and Graduate Education Entrance Exam) and <b>YDS/TOEFL</b> (Foreign Language Exam), they also provide discipline for your preparation process for international exams like the GRE and TOEFL/IELTS.</p>
<p>If your goal is a <b>Ph.D.</b> abroad, completing a master&#8217;s degree with a thesis in Turkey is a significant advantage, as it provides a strong network of academic references and a concrete <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/makale-ve-tez-nedir-nasil-yazilir/">thesis project</a>.</p>
